f="https://open.spotify.com/playlist/37i9dQZF1DX3LyU0mhfqgP" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><img class="thumbnailcard_image__ApqRB" src="/images/120x120/glow-playlist-240.jpg" alt="/images/120x120/glow-playlist-240.jpg"/></a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="driving-change" class="layout-section py-section pb-xl pt-mobile-ml pb-mobile-ml"><div class="container block-container"><div class="row"><div class="col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 col-offset-2 textimage_mobileSwap__DU83h col-12"><div class="mb-m mb-mobile-m mb-0-last"><h3 class="mb-xxxs mb-mobile-xxs bg-color-active size-3 line-120">People drive change</h3><div class="text-mt-0 link-light-bg bg-color-active size-6 line-150 size-7-mobile"><p>Through what they purchase, how they vote, and most importantly, what they say and share. Our work empowers people to drive social change. To use our platform to uplift marginalized voices and amplify important causes. To educate and motivate. To get behind the big social issues and raise awareness of the solutions.</p><p>As a leader in responsible and impactful storytelling, we’re advising our creators and partners on how they can achieve ambitious social goals – pushing culture, acceptance and truth forward.</p></div></div></div><div class="mt-mobile-s col-offset-1 col-8 col-14-mobile col-offset-mobile-5 my-auto"><img src="/images/svg/people-drive-change.svg" alt="" class="image-fluid rounded-20 textimage_svg__KIp_G"/></div></div></div></section><section id="on-spotify" class="layout-section py-section pt-mobile-ml pb-mobile-ml"><div class="container block-container"><div class="row"><div class="col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 textimage_swap__3qGht col-offset-1 col-9"><div class="mb-m mb-mobile-m mb-0-last"><h3 class="mb-xxxs mb-mobile-xxs bg-color-active size-2 line-120">A unique opportunity</h3><div class="text-mt-0 link-light-bg bg-color-active size-6 line-150 size-7-mobile"><p>As the world’s largest audio streaming subscription service, Spotify has a unique opportunity to connect underrepresented and historically marginalized artists and creators to more fans around the world and to put a spotlight on the issues they care about.</p><p>We continue to use our platform to amplify and celebrate creators from underrepresented and historically marginalized communities all year round and to uplift these communities and their causes.</p></div></div></div><div class="mt-mobile-s col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 col-9 col-offset-2 my-auto"><picture><source srcSet="/images/413x580/social_impact_on_spotify-434.webp" media="(max-width: 767px)" type="image/webp"/><source srcSet="/images/413x580/social_impact_on_spotify-434.jpg" media="(max-width: 767px)" type="image/jpeg"/><source srcSet="/images/413x580/social_impact_on_spotify-826.webp" media="(min-width: 768px)" type="image/webp"/><source srcSet="/images/413x580/social_impact_on_spotify-826.jpg" media="(min-width: 768px)" type="image/jpeg"/><img src="/images/413x580/social_impact_on_spotify-826.jpg" alt="" style="max-width:414px;max-height:580px" class="image-fluid rounded-20 textimage_image__nIttw textimage_imageLargeMobile__vDuBQ"/></picture></div></div></div></section><section id="our-initiatives" class="layout-section py-section pt-mobile-ml pb-mobile-ml"><div class="container block-container mb-ml mb-mobile-ml"><div class="row"><div class="col-12 col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 col-12 col-offset-6 text-center"><div class="mb-m mb-mobile-m mb-0-last"><h3 class="mb-xxxs mb-mobile-xxs bg-color-active size-3 line-120">Explore our initiatives</h3><div class="text-mt-0 link-light-bg bg-color-active size-6 line-150 size-7-mobile"><p>We’re using the power of our platform for storytelling and inspiration, and to increase awareness of today’s most pressing issues.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="carousel_blockContainer__X1hfU undefined container block-container fluid mb-0 mb-mobile-0"><div class="drag-carousel"><div class="swiper-container carousel_swiper__jqMlV" modules="[object Object]"><div class="swiper-wrapper"><div class="swiper-slide carousel_swiperSlide___umLf carousel_drag__7kIL1 carousel_smallWide__hslvE"><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><div class="carousel_fadeIn__XeC5Q"><a class="rounded-20 rounded-15-mobile hover-inside defaultcard_container__boBhR defaultcard_cursor__wvFAi clear-button defaultcard_white__9B5wJ defaultcard_smallWide__qdoFa defaultcard_shadow__3PFwc defaultcard_hasLongText__ILAOs" href="https://open.spotify.com/genre/frequency-page" target="_blank"><div class="defaultcard_smallImageContainer__TdAIB"><div class="defaultcard_image__1mfP9 defaultcard_leftImage__1Rj2E" style="background-image:url(&quot;/images/120x120/social_impact_frequency-240.png&quot;)"></div></div><p class="ma-0 mt-s fw-normal size-4 line-120 color-white defaultcard_title__QsVbh"><span class="sr-only">Title:</span>Frequency</p><p class="ma-0 mb-s fw-light size-6 size-8-mobile line-150 color-white defaultcard_longText__t7Hez">Launched in May 2021, Frequency is Spotify’s global initiative and holistic destination for celebrating Black art, entertainment, creativity, culture, and community – both on and off our platform. The mission of Frequency is to create a space that represents the wide spectrum of Black artistry.</p><p class="size-6 size-8-mobile ma-0 no-underline fw-normal color-white bottomlink_container__NPBGI bottomlink_link___hzIf">Listen now</p></a></div></div></div><div class="swiper-slide carousel_swiperSlide___umLf carousel_drag__7kIL1 carousel_smallWide__hslvE"><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><div class="carousel_fadeIn__XeC5Q"><a class="rounded-20 rounded-15-mobile hover-inside defaultcard_container__boBhR defaultcard_cursor__wvFAi clear-button defaultcard_white__9B5wJ defaultcard_smallWide__qdoFa defaultcard_shadow__3PFwc defaultcard_hasLongText__ILAOs" href="https://open.spotify.com/genre/equal-page" target="_blank"><div class="defaultcard_smallImageContainer__TdAIB"><div class="defaultcard_image__1mfP9 defaultcard_leftImage__1Rj2E" style="background-image:url(&quot;/images/120x120/equal-hub-240.jpg&quot;)"></div></div><p class="ma-0 mt-s fw-normal size-4 line-120 color-white defaultcard_title__QsVbh"><span class="sr-only">Title:</span>EQUAL</p><p class="ma-0 mb-s fw-light size-6 size-8-mobile line-150 color-white defaultcard_longText__t7Hez">Also launched back in 2021, EQUAL is a global music program and hub designed to empower and highlight the work of women artists and podcasters. Through EQUAL, we aim to foster equity for women in audio and celebrate their global contributions.</p><p class="size-6 size-8-mobile ma-0 no-underline fw-normal color-white bottomlink_container__NPBGI bottomlink_link___hzIf">Listen now</p></a></div></div></div><div class="swiper-slide carousel_swiperSlide___umLf carousel_drag__7kIL1 carousel_smallWide__hslvE"><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><div class="carousel_fadeIn__XeC5Q"><a class="rounded-20 rounded-15-mobile hover-inside defaultcard_container__boBhR defaultcard_cursor__wvFAi clear-button defaultcard_white__9B5wJ defaultcard_smallWide__qdoFa defaultcard_shadow__3PFwc defaultcard_hasLongText__ILAOs" href="https://open.spotify.com/genre/0JQ5DAqbMKFGnsSfvg90Wo" target="_blank"><div class="defaultcard_smallImageContainer__TdAIB"><div class="defaultcard_image__1mfP9 defaultcard_leftImage__1Rj2E" style="background-image:url(&quot;/images/120x120/GLOW_FTR-Header-240.jpg&quot;)"></div></div><p class="ma-0 mt-s fw-normal size-4 line-120 color-white defaultcard_title__QsVbh"><span class="sr-only">Title:</span>GLOW</p><p class="ma-0 mb-s fw-light size-6 size-8-mobile line-150 color-white defaultcard_longText__t7Hez">GLOW is a global music program celebrating and amplifying LGBTQIA+ artists and creators. It’s our latest initiative to support people of this historically marginalized community of voices and reassert our commitment to equity in audio. It ensures that queer creators, and their contributions to music and culture, are heard and honored year-round.</p><p class="size-6 size-8-mobile ma-0 no-underline fw-normal color-white bottomlink_container__NPBGI bottomlink_link___hzIf">Listen now</p></a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="empowering-the-next-generation" class="layout-section py-section bg-dark-green pt-50% pb-xl pt-mobile-ml pb-mobile-ml LayoutSection_topImageBg__PEXrI"><div id="socialimpact-animation-trigger" class="socialimpact_absoluteContainer__YWGaa"><div class="socialimpact_relativeContainer__iZo_A"><div id="building" class="socialimpact_building__5Ah75"><img src="/esg-animation/SocialImpact/Middleground.svg" alt="building"/></div><div id="rightHill" class="socialimpact_rightHill__HLWZJ"><img src="/esg-animation/SocialImpact/Background.svg" alt="right-hill"/></div><div id="leftHill" class="socialimpact_leftHill__qdUut"><img src="/esg-animation/SocialImpact/Foreground.svg" alt="left-hill"/></div></div></div><div class="container block-container mb-xl mb-mobile-xl"><div class="row"><div class="col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 col-offset-2 textimage_mobileSwap__DU83h col-12"><div class="mb-m mb-mobile-m mb-0-last"><h3 class="mb-xxxs mb-mobile-xxs bg-color-active size-3 line-120">Empowering the next generation</h3><div class="text-mt-0 link-light-bg bg-color-active size-6 line-150 size-7-mobile"><p>We’re committed to removing the barriers that make it harder for creators from marginalized groups to flourish. This is how we do it.</p></div></div></div><div class="mt-mobile-s col-offset-1 col-8 col-14-mobile col-offset-mobile-5 my-auto"><img src="/images/svg/underepresented.svg" alt="" class="image-fluid rounded-20 textimage_svg__KIp_G"/></div></div></div><div class="carousel_blockContainer__X1hfU undefined container block-container fluid mb-0 mb-mobile-0"><div class="drag-carousel"><div class="swiper-container carousel_swiper__jqMlV" modules="[object Object]"><div class="swiper-wrapper"><div class="swiper-slide carousel_swiperSlide___umLf carousel_drag__7kIL1"><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><div class="carousel_fadeIn__XeC5Q"><div class="rounded-20 rounded-15-mobile hover-inside defaultcard_container__boBhR defaultcard_white__9B5wJ defaultcard_hasLongText__ILAOs"><div class="defaultcard_smallImageContainer__TdAIB"><div class="defaultcard_image__1mfP9 defaultcard_smallImage__s01xN" style="background-image:url(&quot;/images/120x120/social_impact_-240.png&quot;)"></div></div><div class="defaultcard_tag__bKVta"><div class="tag_container__KPBGq tag_left__gaI6I tag_white__8ocjD"><div class="tag_badge__RWKrU"><p class="size-7 size-9-mobile fw-normal ma-0 color-white">Hub</p></div></div></div><p class="ma-0 mt-s fw-normal size-4 line-120 color-white defaultcard_title__QsVbh"><span class="sr-only">Title:</span>NextGen</p><p class="ma-0 mb-s fw-light size-6 size-8-mobile line-150 color-white defaultcard_longText__t7Hez mb-0">NextGen is Spotify’s ongoing program designed to infuse, activate, and grow podcast culture on college campuses and make a career in podcasting more accessible. The program is focused on building opportunities in audio and career pipelines for underrepresented students.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="swiper-slide carousel_swiperSlide___umLf carousel_drag__7kIL1"><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><div class="carousel_fadeIn__XeC5Q"><a class="rounded-20 rounded-15-mobile hover-inside defaultcard_container__boBhR defaultcard_cursor__wvFAi clear-button defaultcard_white__9B5wJ defaultcard_hasLongText__ILAOs" href="https://soundup.byspotify.com/" target="_blank"><div class="defaultcard_smallImageContainer__TdAIB"><div class="defaultcard_image__1mfP9 defaultcard_smallImage__s01xN" style="background-image:url(&quot;/images/120x120/social_impact_soundup-240.png&quot;)"></div></div><div class="defaultcard_tag__bKVta"><div class="tag_container__KPBGq tag_left__gaI6I tag_white__8ocjD"><div class="tag_badge__RWKrU"><p class="size-7 size-9-mobile fw-normal ma-0 color-white">Podcast</p></div></div></div><p class="ma-0 mt-s fw-normal size-4 line-120 color-white defaultcard_title__QsVbh"><span class="sr-only">Title:</span>Sound Up</p><p class="ma-0 mb-s fw-light size-6 size-8-mobile line-150 color-white defaultcard_longText__t7Hez">We want to create space for new voices, stories and perspectives in podcasting. Sound Up is our global program for empowering the next generation of podcasters through education, tools, and support. </p><p class="size-6 size-8-mobile ma-0 no-underline fw-normal color-white bottomlink_container__NPBGI bottomlink_link___hzIf">Learn more</p></a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="paying-it-forward" class="layout-section py-section pt-mobile-ml pb-mobile-ml"><div class="container block-container mb-ml mb-mobile-ml"><div class="row"><div class="col-16 col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 col-offset-4 text-center text-center-mobile"><h2 class="size-2 line-100 bg-color-active">Paying it forward</h2></div></div><div class="row mt-xxs mt-mobile-xxs"><div class="col-16 col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 text-mt-0 size-4 line-140 size-6-mobile line-150-mobile bg-color-active col-offset-4 text-center text-center-mobile"><p>Giving guides all aspects of how we show up in the world. </p></div></div></div><div class="container block-container mb-ml mb-mobile-ml"><div class="row"><div class="col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 textimage_swap__3qGht col-offset-1 textimage_mobileSwap__DU83h col-9"><div class="mb-m mb-mobile-m mb-0-last"><div class="text-mt-0 link-light-bg bg-color-active size-6 line-150 size-7-mobile"><p>Our external philanthropy work aligns with our internal work on climate action, civic engagement, mental health, employee wellbeing, and gender and racial equity. Since we launched our giving program in 2020, we’ve committed over $20 million to support non-profits around the world through our employee match program and corporate grant making.</p></div></div><div class="mb-m mb-mobile-m mb-0-last"><h3 class="mb-xxxs mb-mobile-xxs bg-color-active size-4 line-120">Spotify Gives Back</h3><div class="text-mt-0 link-light-bg bg-color-active size-6 line-150 size-7-mobile"><p>Our internal program, Spotify Gives Back, enables employees to contribute to causes they care about and amplify the positive impact of their activities. For us, supercharging the charitable impact that employees can make is one way we foster a sense of belonging within the company and wider community. Through this program, employees can support their favorite nonprofit organizations and participate in company-wide community impact activities. </p></div></div></div><div class="mt-mobile-s col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 col-9 col-offset-2 my-auto"><picture><source srcSet="/images/413x580/social_impact_phil-434.webp" media="(max-width: 767px)" type="image/webp"/><source srcSet="/images/413x580/social_impact_phil-434.jpg" media="(max-width: 767px)" type="image/jpeg"/><source srcSet="/images/413x580/social_impact_phil-826.webp" media="(min-width: 768px)" type="image/webp"/><source srcSet="/images/413x580/social_impact_phil-826.jpg" media="(min-width: 768px)" type="image/jpeg"/><img src="/images/413x580/social_impact_phil-826.jpg" alt="" style="max-width:414px;max-height:580px" class="image-fluid rounded-20 textimage_image__nIttw textimage_imageLargeMobile__vDuBQ"/></picture></div></div></div><div class="container block-container mb-0 mb-mobile-0"><div class="row"><div class="col-12 col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 col-12 col-offset-6 text-center"><div class="mb-m mb-mobile-m mb-0-last"><h3 class="mb-xxxs mb-mobile-xxs bg-color-active size-5 line-120">The program has three components:</h3><div class="text-mt-0 link-light-bg bg-color-active size-6 line-150 size-7-mobile"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="carousel_blockContainer__X1hfU undefined container block-container fluid mb-0 mb-mobile-0"><div class="drag-carousel"><div class="swiper-container carousel_swiper__jqMlV" modules="[object Object]"><div class="swiper-wrapper"><div class="swiper-slide carousel_swiperSlide___umLf carousel_drag__7kIL1"><div class="carousel_fadeIn__XeC5Q"><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><div class="rounded-20 rounded-15-mobile hover-inside p-relative simplecard_container__JygsH simplecard_white__TQp_3 simplecard_shadow__kx_27 simplecard_hasLongText__roZS2"><div class="simplecard_image__BFiih" style="background-image:url(&quot;/images/svg/donation-matching.svg&quot;)"></div><p class="ma-0 mt-xs fw-normal size-4 line-120 color-white simplecard_title__0aOVN"><span class="sr-only">Title:</span>Donations Matching</p><p class="ma-0 mb-0 fw-light size-6 size-8-mobile line-150 color-white simplecard_longText__ps8c8 mb-0">We match donations made to eligible charities either on a 1:1 or 2:1 basis. Every full and part time employee has the ability to get up to 15k USD in donations matched by Spotify.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="swiper-slide carousel_swiperSlide___umLf carousel_drag__7kIL1"><div class="carousel_fadeIn__XeC5Q"><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><div class="rounded-20 rounded-15-mobile hover-inside p-relative simplecard_container__JygsH simplecard_white__TQp_3 simplecard_shadow__kx_27 simplecard_hasLongText__roZS2"><div class="simplecard_image__BFiih" style="background-image:url(&quot;/images/svg/dollar-for-doers.svg&quot;)"></div><p class="ma-0 mt-xs fw-normal size-4 line-120 color-white simplecard_title__0aOVN"><span class="sr-only">Title:</span>Dollars for Doers</p><p class="ma-0 mb-0 fw-light size-6 size-8-mobile line-150 color-white simplecard_longText__ps8c8 mb-0">Spotifiers who volunteer with eligible organizations earn a donation for their service to the organization.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="swiper-slide carousel_swiperSlide___umLf carousel_drag__7kIL1"><div class="carousel_fadeIn__XeC5Q"><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><div class="rounded-20 rounded-15-mobile hover-inside p-relative simplecard_container__JygsH simplecard_white__TQp_3 simplecard_shadow__kx_27 simplecard_hasLongText__roZS2"><div class="simplecard_image__BFiih" style="background-image:url(&quot;/images/svg/impact-day.svg&quot;)"></div><p class="ma-0 mt-xs fw-normal size-4 line-120 color-white simplecard_title__0aOVN"><span class="sr-only">Title:</span>Impact Day</p><p class="ma-0 mb-0 fw-light size-6 size-8-mobile line-150 color-white simplecard_longText__ps8c8 mb-0">One paid day a year for each employee to volunteer at a nonprofit of their choice.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="partnering-up" class="layout-section py-section pt-mobile-ml pb-mobile-ml"><div class="container block-container mb-m mb-mobile-m"><div class="row"><div class="col-16 col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 col-offset-4 text-center text-center-mobile"><h2 class="size-2 line-100 bg-color-active">Partnering up</h2></div></div><div class="row mt-xxs mt-mobile-xxs"><div class="col-16 col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 text-mt-0 size-4 line-140 size-6-mobile line-150-mobile bg-color-active col-offset-4 text-center text-center-mobile"><p>We can’t drive meaningful change on our own. That’s why we choose to support partners doing amazing work around the world.</p></div></div></div><div class="carousel_blockContainer__X1hfU undefined container block-container fluid mb-0 mb-mobile-0"><div class="drag-carousel"><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><div class="popup_container__EMIkb" style="visibility:hidden"><div class="popup_inner__wgnJ3"><div class="popup_closeContainer__V1wpI"><button aria-label="Close" class="clear-button popup_close__zlFgp"></button></div><div class="rounded-20 popup_content__8nEU9"><div class=""><p class="ma-0 mb-m mb-mobile-xxs fw-normal size-4 size-6-mobile line-120 text-center">UNICEF and Ukraine</p><div class="size-6 size-8-mobile line-150 link-light-bg popupcontent_body__pVJgm"><p>Since October 2021, Spotify and UNICEF have worked together to explore ways to use digital media and the power of music and audio to alleviate the mental health distress of young people around the world. Starting with Ukrainian youth and refugees and expanding to other communities in the near future, the goal is to promote psychosocial wellbeing in the long term. </p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><div class="popup_container__EMIkb" style="visibility:hidden"><div class="popup_inner__wgnJ3"><div class="popup_closeContainer__V1wpI"><button aria-label="Close" class="clear-button popup_close__zlFgp"></button></div><div class="rounded-20 popup_content__8nEU9"><div class=""><p class="ma-0 mb-m mb-mobile-xxs fw-normal size-4 size-6-mobile line-120 text-center">Inevitable Foundation</p><div class="size-6 size-8-mobile line-150 link-light-bg popupcontent_body__pVJgm"><p>Inevitable Foundation is committed to shaping a world where disabled storytellers are able to create projects about anything they want, regardless of whether their stories contemplate disability – just one part of their complex identities. Podcasting creates a fruitful starting point for the next generation of disabled storytellers, and this is where Spotify comes in.</p><p>Participants in the Elevate for Podcasters program receive the funding, mentorship, equipment and accommodations they need to level up their careers. The program also includes ongoing support through quarterly check-ins with the Inevitable Foundation team, as well as community-building events where members can expand their professional networks and meet other disabled creatives in podcasting, film and television. </p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><div class="popup_container__EMIkb" style="visibility:hidden"><div class="popup_inner__wgnJ3"><div class="popup_closeContainer__V1wpI"><button aria-label="Close" class="clear-button popup_close__zlFgp"></button></div><div class="rounded-20 popup_content__8nEU9"><div class=""><p class="ma-0 mb-m mb-mobile-xxs fw-normal size-4 size-6-mobile line-120 text-center">4A’s Foundation x Spotify Pulse Fellows</p><div class="size-6 size-8-mobile line-150 link-light-bg popupcontent_body__pVJgm"><p>Unleashing the full scope of creative potential at Spotify means giving as many people as possible a seat at the table. That’s why we partnered with the 4A’s Foundation to launch The Spotify Pulse Fellowship. The initiative sees us partner with programs that are already doing inspiring work supporting, developing, and empowering Black creatives like MAIP(Multicultural Advertising Internship Program), D&AD Shift, Marcus Graham Project, ONE School, and our newest program partner, BLAC Internship. </p><p>By tapping into organizations already created for and by Black creatives, we’re able to find talent for the Spotify PULSE Program and initiate opportunities for individuals in underrepresented communities to gain access to careers at the top.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="swiper-container carousel_swiper__jqMlV" modules="[object Object]"><div class="swiper-wrapper"><div class="swiper-slide carousel_swiperSlide___umLf carousel_drag__7kIL1 carousel_wide__Bg_wd"><div class="carousel_fadeIn__XeC5Q"><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><button class="rounded-20 rounded-15-mobile hover-inside defaultcard_container__boBhR defaultcard_cursor__wvFAi clear-button defaultcard_white__9B5wJ defaultcard_wide__2Gt4v defaultcard_hasLongText__ILAOs"><div class="defaultcard_smallImageContainer__TdAIB"><div class="defaultcard_image__1mfP9 defaultcard_leftImage__1Rj2E" style="background-image:url(&quot;/images/120x120/social_impact_unicef-240.png&quot;)"></div></div><p class="ma-0 mt-s fw-normal size-4 line-120 color-white defaultcard_title__QsVbh"><span class="sr-only">Title:</span>UNICEF and Ukraine</p><p class="ma-0 mb-s fw-light size-6 size-8-mobile line-150 color-white defaultcard_longText__t7Hez">Spotify and UNICEF have embarked on a multiyear partnership that will explore innovative ways to support the mental health and wellbeing of young people, and their caregivers, including those affected by war.</p><p class="size-6 size-8-mobile ma-0 no-underline fw-normal color-white bottomlink_container__NPBGI bottomlink_plus__3w8tn bottomlink_link___hzIf">Learn more</p></button></div></div></div><div class="swiper-slide carousel_swiperSlide___umLf carousel_drag__7kIL1 carousel_wide__Bg_wd"><div class="carousel_fadeIn__XeC5Q"><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><button class="rounded-20 rounded-15-mobile hover-inside defaultcard_container__boBhR defaultcard_cursor__wvFAi clear-button defaultcard_white__9B5wJ defaultcard_wide__2Gt4v defaultcard_hasLongText__ILAOs"><div class="defaultcard_smallImageContainer__TdAIB"><div class="defaultcard_image__1mfP9 defaultcard_leftImage__1Rj2E" style="background-image:url(&quot;/images/120x120/social_impact_inevitable-240.png&quot;)"></div></div><p class="ma-0 mt-s fw-normal size-4 line-120 color-white defaultcard_title__QsVbh"><span class="sr-only">Title:</span>Inevitable Foundation</p><p class="ma-0 mb-s fw-light size-6 size-8-mobile line-150 color-white defaultcard_longText__t7Hez">Spotify partnered with the Inevitable Foundation to launch Elevate for Podcasters, a program that empowers professional podcasters with disabilities to level up their careers.</p><p class="size-6 size-8-mobile ma-0 no-underline fw-normal color-white bottomlink_container__NPBGI bottomlink_plus__3w8tn bottomlink_link___hzIf">Learn more</p></button></div></div></div><div class="swiper-slide carousel_swiperSlide___umLf carousel_drag__7kIL1 carousel_wide__Bg_wd"><div class="carousel_fadeIn__XeC5Q"><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><button class="rounded-20 rounded-15-mobile hover-inside defaultcard_container__boBhR defaultcard_cursor__wvFAi clear-button defaultcard_white__9B5wJ defaultcard_wide__2Gt4v defaultcard_hasLongText__ILAOs"><div class="defaultcard_smallImageContainer__TdAIB"><div class="defaultcard_image__1mfP9 defaultcard_leftImage__1Rj2E" style="background-image:url(&quot;/images/120x120/social_impact_4a-240.png&quot;)"></div></div><p class="ma-0 mt-s fw-normal size-4 line-120 color-white defaultcard_title__QsVbh"><span class="sr-only">Title:</span>4A’s Foundation x Spotify Pulse Fellows</p><p class="ma-0 mb-s fw-light size-6 size-8-mobile line-150 color-white defaultcard_longText__t7Hez">A cocreated, yearlong creative development program for Black professionals with one to three years of professional experience in the advertising industry.</p><p class="size-6 size-8-mobile ma-0 no-underline fw-normal color-white bottomlink_container__NPBGI bottomlink_plus__3w8tn bottomlink_link___hzIf">Learn more</p></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="civic-community-engagement" class="layout-section py-section pt-mobile-ml pb-mobile-ml"><div class="container block-container mb-ml mb-mobile-ml"><div class="row"><div class="col-16 col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 col-offset-4 text-center text-center-mobile"><h2 class="size-2 line-100 bg-color-active">Civic and Community Engagement</h2></div></div><div class="row mt-xxs mt-mobile-xxs"><div class="col-16 col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 text-mt-0 size-4 line-140 size-6-mobile line-150-mobile bg-color-active col-offset-4 text-center text-center-mobile"><p>As our world experiences unprecedented shifts, our commitment to making a positive social impact grows ever stronger.</p></div></div></div><div class="container block-container mb-ml mb-mobile-ml"><div class="row"><div class="col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 textimage_swap__3qGht col-offset-1 textimage_mobileSwap__DU83h col-9"><div class="mb-m mb-mobile-m mb-0-last"><div class="text-mt-0 link-light-bg bg-color-active size-6 line-150 size-7-mobile"><p>As a global institution, we have the responsibility and the opportunity to show up in a meaningful way for people, culture, the audio industry and our band members.</p></div></div></div><div class="mt-mobile-s col-9 col-offset-2 col-14-mobile col-offset-mobile-5 my-auto"><img src="/images/svg/cce.svg" alt="" class="image-fluid rounded-20 textimage_svg__KIp_G"/></div></div></div><div class="carousel_blockContainer__X1hfU carousel_has-fadeUp-outside__Ts9NF container block-container fluid mb-0 mb-mobile-0"><div class="drag-carousel"><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><div class="popup_container__EMIkb" style="visibility:hidden"><div class="popup_inner__wgnJ3"><div class="popup_closeContainer__V1wpI"><button aria-label="Close" class="clear-button popup_close__zlFgp"></button></div><div class="rounded-20 popup_content__8nEU9"><div class=""><p class="ma-0 mb-m mb-mobile-xxs fw-normal size-4 size-6-mobile line-120 text-center">Responsible storytelling</p><div class="size-6 size-8-mobile line-150 link-light-bg popupcontent_body__pVJgm popupcontent_black__rt4wn"><p>For Spotify, media responsibility means supercharging the impact of our audio platform through accurate, trustworthy and progressive storytelling. We prioritize stories from historically marginalized communities and focus on issues that resonate with our listeners.<br><br>We do this in three ways:<br><br><ul style><li>Increasing the reach of potentially impactful content</li><li>Connecting stories to opportunities for listeners to take real action<li>Showcasing positive depictions of historically marginalized and underrepresented communities in order to shift narratives</li></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><div class="popup_container__EMIkb" style="visibility:hidden"><div class="popup_inner__wgnJ3"><div class="popup_closeContainer__V1wpI"><button aria-label="Close" class="clear-button popup_close__zlFgp"></button></div><div class="rounded-20 popup_content__8nEU9"><div class=""><p class="ma-0 mb-m mb-mobile-xxs fw-normal size-4 size-6-mobile line-120 text-center">Participating in the democratic process</p><div class="size-6 size-8-mobile line-150 link-light-bg popupcontent_body__pVJgm"><p>We bring messages about civic engagement to our audience wherever they are – and from the voices they trust the most. Our campaigns are nonpartisan and focus on making voting easier and more exciting for our audience. </p><p>We’ve been running voter engagement campaigns since 2016. Initially, we focused our efforts on the US and in the EU, expanding into more countries every year. Over that time, we’ve reached nearly 57 million listeners worldwide, encouraging people globally to play their part in their local elections. These campaigns drove nearly 4 million visits to resources on civic engagement so far.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="swiper-container carousel_swiper__jqMlV" modules="[object Object]"><div class="swiper-wrapper"><div class="swiper-slide carousel_swiperSlide___umLf carousel_drag__7kIL1 carousel_wide__Bg_wd"><div class="carousel_fadeIn__XeC5Q"><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><button class="rounded-20 rounded-15-mobile hover-inside defaultcard_container__boBhR defaultcard_cursor__wvFAi clear-button defaultcard_album-pink__yEKSf defaultcard_wide__2Gt4v defaultcard_hasLongText__ILAOs"><span class="defaultcard_spacer__e0Dn2 defaultcard_hasCta__YfZqx"></span><p class="ma-0 mt-s fw-normal size-4 line-120 color-white defaultcard_title__QsVbh"><span class="sr-only">Title:</span>Responsible storytelling</p><p class="ma-0 mb-s fw-light size-6 size-8-mobile line-150 color-white defaultcard_longText__t7Hez">For Spotify, media responsibility means supercharging the impact of our audio platform through accurate, trustworthy and progressive storytelling.</p><span class="defaultcard_spacer__e0Dn2 is-hidden-desktop defaultcard_hasCta__YfZqx"></span><p class="size-6 size-8-mobile ma-0 no-underline fw-normal color-white bottomlink_container__NPBGI bottomlink_plus__3w8tn bottomlink_link___hzIf">Learn more</p></button></div></div></div><div class="swiper-slide carousel_swiperSlide___umLf carousel_drag__7kIL1 carousel_wide__Bg_wd"><div class="carousel_fadeIn__XeC5Q"><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><button class="rounded-20 rounded-15-mobile hover-inside defaultcard_container__boBhR defaultcard_cursor__wvFAi clear-button defaultcard_album-pink__yEKSf defaultcard_wide__2Gt4v defaultcard_hasLongText__ILAOs"><span class="defaultcard_spacer__e0Dn2 defaultcard_hasCta__YfZqx"></span><p class="ma-0 mt-s fw-normal size-4 line-120 color-white defaultcard_title__QsVbh"><span class="sr-only">Title:</span>Participating in the democratic process</p><p class="ma-0 mb-s fw-light size-6 size-8-mobile line-150 color-white defaultcard_longText__t7Hez">Our mission is simple. We want to help consumers, creators, and employees to feel empowered to vote – all while providing real, actionable solutions to problems.</p><span class="defaultcard_spacer__e0Dn2 is-hidden-desktop defaultcard_hasCta__YfZqx"></span><p class="size-6 size-8-mobile ma-0 no-underline fw-normal color-white bottomlink_container__NPBGI bottomlink_plus__3w8tn bottomlink_link___hzIf">Learn more</p></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="layout-section py-section"><div class="container block-container"><div class="row"><div class="col-24"><h2 class="bg-color-active line-110 size-3 text-center mb-m mb-mobile-m">Quick clicks</h2><a class="mb-xs mb-mobile-xs quicklink_container__XU717" href="/diversity-equity-impact/climate-action"><p class="ma-0 color-gray-400 is-visible-desktop is-hidden-mobile bg-color-active size-4 size-6-mobile line-140 quicklink_text__fQxds">Discover more about <span>Climate Action</span></p><p class="ma-0 color-gray-400 is-hidden-desktop is-visible-mobile bg-color-active size-4 size-6-mobile line-140 quicklink_text__fQxds"><span>Climate Action</span></p><div class="quicklink_button__B3y8U"><button aria-label="Go to page" style="transform:rotate(nulldeg)" class="arrows_filled__L4ANR arrows_dark__M7afL undefined arrows_darkBackground__ZtZM9"></button></div></a><a class="mb-xs mb-mobile-xs quicklink_container__XU717" href="/diversity-equity-impact/mental-health"><p class="ma-0 color-gray-400 is-visible-desktop is-hidden-mobile bg-color-active size-4 size-6-mobile line-140 quicklink_text__fQxds">See our <span>Mental Health</span> initiatives</p><p class="ma-0 color-gray-400 is-hidden-desktop is-visible-mobile bg-color-active size-4 size-6-mobile line-140 quicklink_text__fQxds"><span>Mental Health</span></p><div class="quicklink_button__B3y8U"><button aria-label="Go to page" style="transform:rotate(nulldeg)" class="arrows_filled__L4ANR arrows_dark__M7afL undefined arrows_darkBackground__ZtZM9"></button></div></a><a class="mb-xs mb-mobile-xs quicklink_container__XU717" href="/diversity-equity-impact/diversity-equity-inclusion-belonging"><p class="ma-0 color-gray-400 is-visible-desktop is-hidden-mobile bg-color-active size-4 size-6-mobile line-140 quicklink_text__fQxds">Read about <span>Diversity, Equity & Inclusion</span></p><p class="ma-0 color-gray-400 is-hidden-desktop is-visible-mobile bg-color-active size-4 size-6-mobile line-140 quicklink_text__fQxds">About <span>belonging</span></p><div class="quicklink_button__B3y8U"><button aria-label="Go to page" style="transform:rotate(nulldeg)" class="arrows_filled__L4ANR arrows_dark__M7afL undefined arrows_darkBackground__ZtZM9"></button></div></a></div></div></div></section></main><footer id="js-footer" class="footer_container__5R4W_"><div class="container p-relative color-white"><div class="is-hidden-mobile footer_scrollButton__EP8vS"><button aria-label="Scroll to top" style="transform:rotate(-90deg)" class="arrows_filled__L4ANR arrows_light__pwMV0 undefined"></button></div><div class="row"><div class="col-offset-10 col-4 col-offset-mobile-0 col-24-mobile text-center mb-50 mb-mobile-xs"><img class="footer_icon__O4zRj" src="/icons/icon-footer.svg" alt=""/></div><div class="col-offset-6 col-12 col-offset-mobile-0 col-24-mobile text-center"><h